Num PDSCH Decode (Record 0).name: Num PDSCH Decode (Record 0)
Num PDSCH Decode (Record 0).description:
Number of PDSCH decode completed per CA. This equals total
number of TB decoded. It is the sum of crc_pass + crc_fail +
tb_discard

Num CRC Pass TB (Record 0).name: Num CRC Pass TB (Record 0)
Num CRC Pass TB (Record 0).description: Number of CRC pass TB per CA

Num CRC Fail TB (Record 0).name: Num CRC Fail TB (Record 0)
Num CRC Fail TB (Record 0).description: Number of CRC fail TB per CA

Num ReTx (Record 0).name: Num ReTx (Record 0)
Num ReTx (Record 0).description: Number of TB retransmissions per CA

CRC Pass TB Bytes (Record 0).name: CRC Pass TB Bytes (Record 0)
CRC Pass TB Bytes (Record 0).description: Number of CRC pass TB bytes per CA

CRC Fail TB Bytes (Record 0).name: CRC Fail TB Bytes (Record 0)
CRC Fail TB Bytes (Record 0).description: Number of CRC fail TB bytes per CA

TB Bytes (Record 0).name: TB Bytes (Record 0)
TB Bytes (Record 0).description:
Total number of decoded TB bytes per CA. Sum of crc_pass
and crc_fail bytes

BLER (Record 0).name: BLER (Record 0)
BLER (Record 0).description: validation: 0 != ."Num CRC Pass TB" + ."Num CRC Fail TB"
